# [2023 UPDATE] INTRODUCTION

## #0.2 What is Firebase

- Firebase - 백엔드 서비스 서비스 혹은 앱 개발 플랫폼, No-SQL

## \***\*#0.3 When Not To Use Firebase\*\***

- 앱이 성장해서 커스텀해야 하는 상황에선 no-use ex) 특정 영역의 최적화 like Champagne Problems

# [2023 UPDATE] SETUP

## #1.0 Installation

- `npm create vite@latest`
- `npm i react-router-dom@6.14.2`
- `npm i styled-reset`
- `npm i styled-components@6.0.7`
- `npm i @types/styled-components -D`

## #1.1 Routing

- 기본 routing과 styled-components 구조
  ```tsx
  import { createBrowserRouter, RouterProvider } from "react-router-dom";
  import Layout from "./components/Layout";
  import Home from "./routes/Home";
  import Profile from "./routes/Profile";
  import Login from "./routes/Login";
  import CreateAccount from "./routes/CreateAccount";
  import { createGlobalStyle } from "styled-components";
  import reset from "styled-reset";

  const router = createBrowserRouter([
    {
      path: "/",
      element: <Layout />,
      children: [
        {
          path: "",
          element: <Home />,
        },
        {
          path: "profile",
          element: <Profile />,
        },
      ],
    },
    {
      path: "/login",
      element: <Login />,
    },
    {
      path: "create-account",
      element: <CreateAccount />,
    },
  ]);

  const GlobalStyles = createGlobalStyle`
    ${reset};
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
  
    body {
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
      // font-family: 
    }
  `;

  function App() {
    return (
      <>
        <GlobalStyles />
        <RouterProvider router={router} />
      </>
    );
  }

  export default App;
  ```

